dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Mount Sizer quadrangle, Santa Clara County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle MOUNT SIZER, CA 1955, PHOTOREVISED 1971, PHOTOINSPECTED 1978." "First printing, June 2005." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
